---
import Layout from "$/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Widgets" description="Sample widgets built with BeerCSS and the Stackific custom CSS framework.">
  <main id="main">
    <section id="top" class="container-lg mt-9 p-1 m:p-2 l:p-5">
      <h1 class="text-6 m:text-7 lh--1 fw-7">Widgets</h1>
      <p class="text-2 mt-3">Sample widgets built with BeerCSS and our utility classes.</p>

      <nav class="wrap mt-5">
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-flank">Flank</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-empty-centered">Empty — centered</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-empty-actions">Empty — action grid</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-empty-invite">Empty — invite list</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-leaderboard">Leaderboard — single</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-leaderboard2">Leaderboard — split</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-action-panels">Action panels</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-order-history">Order history</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-invoice-table">Invoice table</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#cmp-shopping-cart">Shopping cart</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="container-lg mt-9 p-1 m:p-2 l:p-5" aria-labelledby="cmp-flank">
      <nav><h2 id="cmp-flank" class="text-4 fw-7 max">Flank</h2><a class="chip small" href="#top"><i>arrow_upward</i><span>Top</span></a></nav>
      <p class="text-1 mt-2">Leading avatar flanked by a stack of text. BeerCSS <code>ul.list</code> with leading media, sized and spaced with our utilities.</p>

      <div class="tabs right-align mt-5">
        <a class="active" data-ui="#flank-preview">Preview</a>
        <a data-ui="#flank-code">Code</a>
      </div>

      <div class="page active" id="flank-preview">
        <ul class="list border round mt-3">
          <li class="py-4 top-align">
            <img class="circle" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553284966-19b8815c7817?q=20" alt="" />
            <div class="max">
              <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Gandalf</strong>
              <p class="text-1 mt-1">All we have to decide is what to do with the time that is given to us. There are other forces at work in this world, Frodo, besides the will of evil.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="py-4 top-align">
            <img class="circle" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553284966-19b8815c7817?q=20" alt="" />
            <div class="max">
              <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Boromir</strong>
              <p class="text-1 mt-1">One does not simply walk into Mordor. Its Black Gates are guarded by more than just Orcs. There is evil there that does not sleep, and the Great Eye is ever watchful.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="py-4 top-align">
            <img class="circle" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553284966-19b8815c7817?q=20" alt="" />
            <div class="max">
              <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Galadriel</strong>
              <p class="text-1 mt-1">The world is changed. I feel it in the water. I feel it in the earth. I smell it in the air. Much that once was is lost, for none now live who remember it.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="page" id="flank-code">
        <pre class="border round mt-3 p-4"><code>{`<ul class="list border round">
  <li class="py-4 top-align">
    <img class="circle" src="/avatar.jpg" alt="" />
    <div class="max">
      <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Gandalf</strong>
      <p class="text-1 mt-1">All we have to decide is what to do with the time that is given to us...</p>
    </div>
  </li>
  <!-- more <li> rows -->
</ul>`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container-lg mt-9 p-1 m:p-2 l:p-5" aria-labelledby="cmp-empty-centered">
      <nav><h2 id="cmp-empty-centered" class="text-4 fw-7 max">Empty state — centered</h2><a class="chip small" href="#top"><i>arrow_upward</i><span>Top</span></a></nav>
      <p class="text-1 mt-2">Icon, headline, supporting text, and a single primary action. BeerCSS <code>article</code> + <code>center-align</code>.</p>

      <div class="tabs right-align mt-5">
        <a class="active" data-ui="#empty1-preview">Preview</a>
        <a data-ui="#empty1-code">Code</a>
      </div>

      <div class="page active" id="empty1-preview">
        <article class="no-elevate border round center-align py-9 mt-3">
          <i class="extra">backpack</i>
          <h3 class="text-3 fw-7 mt-3">No Kits</h3>
          <p class="text-1 mt-2">Manage all of your project's icons in a kit.</p>
          <nav class="center-align mt-4">
            <button><i>add</i><span>Add Kit</span></button>
          </nav>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="page" id="empty1-code">
        <pre class="border round mt-3 p-4"><code>{`<article class="no-elevate border round center-align py-9">
  <i class="extra">backpack</i>
  <h3 class="text-3 fw-7 mt-3">No Kits</h3>
  <p class="text-1 mt-2">Manage all of your project's icons in a kit.</p>
  <nav class="center-align mt-4">
    <button><i>add</i><span>Add Kit</span></button>
  </nav>
</article>`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container-lg mt-9 p-1 m:p-2 l:p-5" aria-labelledby="cmp-empty-actions">
      <nav><h2 id="cmp-empty-actions" class="text-4 fw-7 max">Empty state — action grid</h2><a class="chip small" href="#top"><i>arrow_upward</i><span>Top</span></a></nav>
      <p class="text-1 mt-2">Card with a header, a grid of "create" actions, and a divider footer link. BeerCSS <code>article</code> + <code>grid</code>.</p>

      <div class="tabs right-align mt-5">
        <a class="active" data-ui="#empty2-preview">Preview</a>
        <a data-ui="#empty2-code">Code</a>
      </div>

      <div class="page active" id="empty2-preview">
        <article class="no-elevate border round p-0 mt-3">
          <header class="p-5"><h3 class="text-3 fw-7">Projects</h3></header>
          <div class="px-5 pb-5">
            <p class="text-1">You haven't created a project yet. Get started by selecting a template or start with a blank canvas.</p>
            <div class="grid mt-5">
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large yellow"><i>sticky_note_2</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Quick Note <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">Jot down any idea. Will it make sense later? Who knows.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large red"><i>checklist</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Checklist <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">The ultimate tool for looking busy.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large purple"><i>grid_on</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Spreadsheet <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">Endless rows and columns of tiny, soul-crushing numbers.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large orange"><i>slideshow</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Slideshow <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">Dramatic transitions make everything seem more official.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large green"><i>edit_note</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Form <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">Collect the deepest personal details and darkest secrets.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
              <div class="s12 m6">
                <nav class="top-align">
                  <button class="circle large blue"><i>image</i></button>
                  <div class="max">
                    <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Photo Album <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
                    <p class="text-1 mt-1">Curate your best memories or most basic food pictures.</p>
                  </div>
                </nav>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <footer class="p-5"><a href="#" class="text-1 fw-6">Or start with a blank canvas <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></a></footer>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="page" id="empty2-code">
        <pre class="border round mt-3 p-4"><code>{`<article class="no-elevate border round p-0">
  <header class="p-5"><h3 class="text-3 fw-7">Projects</h3></header>
  <div class="px-5 pb-5">
    <p class="text-1">You haven't created a project yet...</p>
    <div class="grid mt-5">
      <div class="s12 m6">
        <nav class="top-align">
          <button class="circle large yellow"><i>sticky_note_2</i></button>
          <div class="max">
            <strong class="text-2 fw-7">Create a Quick Note <i class="text-1">arrow_forward</i></strong>
            <p class="text-1 mt-1">Jot down any idea...</p>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <!-- more s12 m6 cells -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="p-5"><a href="#" class="text-1 fw-6">Or start with a blank canvas →</a></footer>
</article>`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container-lg mt-9 mb-10 p-1 m:p-2 l:p-5" aria-labelledby="cmp-empty-invite">
      <nav><h2 id="cmp-empty-invite" class="text-4 fw-7 max">Empty state — invite list</h2><a class="chip small" href="#top"><i>arrow_upward</i><span>Top</span></a></nav>
      <p class="text-1 mt-2">Card with a header, an inline invite field, and a list of suggested members. BeerCSS <code>field</code> + <code>ul.list</code>.</p>

